<section class="services-list" aria-label="Our Digital Services">
    <article class="service-card">
        <div class="service-number" aria-hidden="true">01</div>
        <div class="service-content">
            <h2>
                <span class="lang-en">WEB DEVELOPMENT</span>
                <span class="lang-id">PENGEMBANGAN WEB</span>
            </h2>
            <p class="lang-en">
                Custom, high-performance web applications built with modern
                technologies like React, Next.js, and Astro. We create scalable
                solutions that grow with your business, ensuring fast load times
                and seamless user experiences.
            </p>
            <p class="lang-id">
                Aplikasi web kustom berskala tinggi yang dibangun dengan
                teknologi modern seperti React, Next.js, dan Astro. Kami
                merancang solusi terukur yang berkembang bersama bisnis Anda,
                memastikan waktu muat cepat dan pengalaman pengguna yang mulus.
            </p>
        </div>
    </article>

    <article class="service-card">
        <div class="service-number" aria-hidden="true">02</div>
        <div class="service-content">
            <h2>
                <span class="lang-en">UI/UX DESIGN</span>
                <span class="lang-id">DESAIN UI/UX</span>
            </h2>
            <p class="lang-en">
                Beautiful, intuitive user interfaces focused on conversion and
                usability. We design engaging digital products that delight your
                users and effectively communicate your brand's unique value
                proposition.
            </p>
            <p class="lang-id">
                Antarmuka pengguna yang indah dan intuitif yang berfokus pada
                konversi dan kegunaan. Kami merancang produk digital menarik
                yang memuaskan pengguna Anda dan secara efektif
                mengkomunikasikan proposisi nilai unik dari merek Anda.
            </p>
        </div>
    </article>

    <article class="service-card">
        <div class="service-number" aria-hidden="true">03</div>
        <div class="service-content">
            <h2>
                <span class="lang-en">DEPLOYMENT & MAINTENANCE</span>
                <span class="lang-id">DEPLOYMENT & PEMELIHARAAN</span>
            </h2>
            <p class="lang-en">
                Reliable cloud hosting setup, CI/CD pipeline configuration, and
                ongoing technical support. We ensure your application remains
                secure, up-to-date, and performs flawlessly under any amount of
                traffic.
            </p>
            <p class="lang-id">
                Pengaturan hosting cloud yang andal, konfigurasi pipeline CI/CD,
                dan dukungan teknis berkelanjutan. Kami memastikan aplikasi Anda
                tetap aman, terbaru, dan bekerja dengan sempurna di bawah
                berbagai tingkat lalu lintas pengunjung.
            </p>
        </div>
    </article>
</section>

<style>
    .services-list {
        display: flex;
        flex-direction: column;
        gap: 3rem;
        margin-bottom: 5rem;
    }

    .service-card {
        display: grid;
        grid-template-columns: 1fr;
        gap: 1.5rem;
        padding-top: 2rem;
        border-top: 1px solid var(--color-border);
    }

    @media (min-width: 768px) {
        .service-card {
            grid-template-columns: auto 1fr;
            gap: 4rem;
        }
    }

    .service-number {
        font-family: var(--font-heading);
        font-weight: 800;
        font-size: 3rem;
        color: var(--color-text-muted);
        opacity: 0.5;
        line-height: 1;
    }

    @media (min-width: 768px) {
        .service-number {
            font-size: 5rem;
        }
    }

    .service-content h2 {
        font-size: 1.8rem;
        margin-top: 0;
        margin-bottom: 1rem;
        text-transform: uppercase;
    }

    .service-content p {
        font-size: 1.1rem;
        line-height: 1.8;
        color: var(--color-text);
        margin: 0;
    }

    /* Language Visibility */
    .lang-en,
    .lang-id {
        display: none;
        animation: fadeIn 0.3s ease;
    }

    :global(html:not([data-lang])) .lang-en {
        display: block;
    }

    :global(html[data-lang="en"]) .lang-en {
        display: block;
    }

    :global(html[data-lang="id"]) .lang-id {
        display: block;
    }

    @keyframes fadeIn {
        from {
            opacity: 0;
            transform: translateY(5px);
        }
        to {
            opacity: 1;
            transform: translateY(0);
        }
    }
</style>
